<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>英语-VICE</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 01:07:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阴谋论者已经试图（但失败了）抹黑阿尔忒弥斯二号任务</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/conspiracy-theorists-are-already-trying-and-failing-to-discredit-the-artemis-ii-mission/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;现代互联网上的专业阴谋论者通过散布一些关于长期确定的科学的荒谬谎言来赚钱，从散布恐惧中获利，正如预期的那样，他们全力出击。自从美国宇航局的阿耳忒弥斯二号任务成功地将其机组人员绕月球一周以获取特写镜头以来，他们一直感到不安[...]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/conspiracy-theorists-are-already-trying-and-failing-to-discredit-the-artemis-ii-mission/"&gt;阴谋论者已经试图（并且失败）抹黑阿耳忒弥斯二号任务的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/conspiracy-theorists-are-already-trying-and-failing-to-discredit-the-artemis-ii-mission/</guid></item><item><title>在出现风险之前，你可以重新加热剩菜多少次？</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/how-many-times-can-you-reheat-leftovers-before-it-gets-risky/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;冰箱里装满了剩菜，确实让人感到很舒服。晚饭就处理好了。午餐已经准备好了。但在第三天左右，舒适开始变成焦虑——心算变得有点创造性。如果你现在重新加热，时钟会重置吗？还要再买几天吗？答案是否定的。和食品安全[...]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/how-many-times-can-you-reheat-leftovers-before-it-gets-risky/"&gt;在有风险之前，你可以重新加热剩菜多少次？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 23:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/how-many-times-can-you-reheat-leftovers-before-it-gets-risky/</guid></item><item><title>我的强迫症患者一直试图推销我的 5 个谎言（无论我多么努力地忽略它们）</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/5-lies-my-ocd-keeps-trying-to-sell-me-no-matter-how-hard-i-try-to-ignore-them/</link><